{"tid":275297,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"李小加：債券通南向2年內不會開通 (09:45)","createTime":"2017-06-08T02:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T03:26:56.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b3f90569dca0d97ed022dd61e633fa2e1a7000","tid":275297,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:23:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=b7q%2BM6LLEIpiItzOj1ChkQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=f2d92abf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】香港交易所(00388)行政總裁李小加稱，「債券通」南向於2年內不會開通。<br />\n<br />\n「債券通」已確認初期先開通「北向」交易，不設額度限制，暫時亦只容許機構投資者參與。「債券通」的意義在於利用港交所的交易平台及金管局的結算系統，讓境外投資者買內地債券，推動內地債市的開放和國際化。<br />\n<br />\n對於有報道稱，債券通會在七一前後實施，人民銀行與金管局的聯合公告表示，在完成相關規則和系統建設、回應市場參與者實際需求及獲得相關監管許可後，便會正式啟動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170608/20170608094521fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170608%2F20170608094521fi.html&d=b7q%2BM6LLEIpiItzOj1ChkQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=870c93f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170608/20170608094521fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"82864d2f387db25e9f0b136391a046d24c90397d","tid":275297,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:28:41.000Z","msg":"香港d ibond就香港人自己啃曬<br />\n<br />\n大陸d陰司紙就推你去買<br />\n<br />\n你都得㗎喇小李<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38a02bef361cc71aa03845e4c687a7bbef57a1f","tid":275297,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:32:20.000Z","msg":"mpf唔知會唔會投入去，隨時出現債務違約 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bbdf1062d33bc72a31ac984442c8989d249c92","tid":275297,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:36:03.000Z","msg":"債劵要畀息, 家下佢分分鐘外匯唔夠, 仲要派外匯息, 一違約就成個支那貨幣就真係變廢紙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcea4976af77a09e19773f1